<item>
            <title>[DERBY-6401] Create a test option to stop running Junit tests after first failure or error</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/DERBY-6401</link>
                <project id="10594" key="DERBY">Derby</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Sometimes when debugging issues, it would be convenient to have the tests stop after the first failure or error. Add System property option derby.tests.stopAfterFirstFail to do this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
